high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter top above the dishwasher, just past the refrigerator.
Pick up the loaf of bread to the right of the toaster.
Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the knife's on the counter.
Place the bread on the counter to the left of the knife's.
Pick up the knife closest to the fork on the right, located on the counter.
Cut the loaf of bread on the counter, into slices.
Place the knife back on the counter, between the butter knife and the fork.
Pick up the end slice of bread on the counter.
Turn to your right and go to the microwave, above the stove, on your left.
Place the slice of bread in the microwave, warm it, and remove it from the microwave.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the counter with the coffee maker on it.
Place the slice of bread on the counter, between the salt and the credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm slice of bread on the counter.

high_descs: Look around and face the counter at the left.
pick up the bread at the counter beside the toaster.
Look around and face to the counter.
Put the bread at the counter.
Pick up the knife at the counter.
Slice the bread at the counter.
Put back the knife at the counter.
Pick up one slice of the bread.
walk to the left and face the stove.
Open the microwave and put the bread inside. Heat it for few seconds and get it out.
Turn right and face the counter at the left.
Put the bread at the counter beside the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Heat one piece of the slice bread and bring it beside the coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn around and walk halfway across the room and then turn left to face the bread on the counter.
Pick up the bread on the counter.
Step to the right and face the counter.
Place the bread back into it's original spot on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the bread on the counter into slices.
Place the knife back into it's spot on the counter.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Take a step to the right and face the microwave above the stove.
Head the slice of bread in the microwave and then remove it.
Take a step to the right and face the counter to the right of the stove.
Place the slice of bread on the counter to the right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: TO heat a slice of bread and place it on the counter to the right of the stove.
